gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Hawks 109, Spurs 99
gameRecap.excerpt: The Hawks defeated the Spurs, 109-99. Trae Young led the Hawks with 36 points, 13 assists, and six rebounds, with Jalen Johnson adding 16 points, 10 rebounds, and seven assists in the victory. Victor Wembanyama tallied 26 points, 13 rebounds, and five blocks for the Spurs in the defeat. The Hawks improve to 16-23 in the regular season, while the Spurs fall to 7-32.
